Overview

"Every advisor considering the RIA model is different. That's why our Bridge to Independence program is tailored to your needs."
Scott Collins, Director, Brokerage Independence, TD Ameritrade Institutional

Watch:
Step-by-step Transition Support





Our Bridge to Independence program supports you through each phase of the transition process. We assist you in a tailored way to help you meet your specific needs, ambitions, and business vision.













Why independence?
By becoming an RIA, you'll gain more control over your business and compensation—and more flexibility to meet your clients' wealth management needs.
Explore the benefits


Already an RIA?
We're more than a custodian. Our business has been built by and for RIAs from the ground up. We don't compete with you in the same way that other custodians do—Independent RIAs are TD Ameritrade Institutional’s wealth management channel. We dedicate all of our resources toward understanding where you're coming from and where you're going. Then, we bring you the support, tools and resources you need.
See how we support RIAs


















